Bishop '''Gerald Almeida''' (born March 7, 1946) is the current [[Roman Catholic]] Bishop of [[Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh]], India since 2001.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/djblp.html |title=Jabalpur (Diocese) [Catholic-Hierarchy] |publisher=[[Catholic-Hierarchy.org]] |accessdate=December 19, 2015}}</ref>

==Early life==
Bishop Gerald Almeida was born on March 7, 1946 at [[Udyavar]] a small town near [[Mangalore]]. He was ordained a priest in 1974.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/balm.html |title=Bishop Gerald Almeida [Catholic-Hierarchy] |publisher=Catholic-Hierarchy.org |accessdate=December 19, 2015}}</ref>

