In [[demonology]], '''Vapula''' is a powerful Great Duke of [[Hell]] that commands thirty-six [[wikt:Legion|legions]] of [[demon]]s. He teaches [[philosophy]], [[mechanics]], and sciences.

Vapula is depicted as a [[griffin]]-winged [[lion]].

